## 🔄 Automatisation

### Schedule Quotidien (OpenClaw)

```json
{
  "name": "beautiful-websites-daily",
  "schedule": {
    "kind": "cron",
    "expr": "0 14 * * *"
  },
  "payload": {
    "kind": "agentTurn",
    "message": "Run beautiful websites pipeline for [TYPE] in [VILLE], 50 businesses"
  }
}
```

### Variables à Personnaliser

- `[TYPE]` → wedding venues, nail salons, restaurants...
- `[VILLE]` → Sydney, Paris, Lyon...
- `[QUANTITE]` → 50, 100...

